reviewText: this is a great workout when i do not have time to make it to the gym and need a quick ab workout

Buyers Beware: This workout is a compilation of the other QuickFix workout DVDs, with NO new material. The workouts (along with their corresponding previous DVD) are as follows: Total Abs with Tracy York (Total Mix: Combination Yoga & Pilates Workout) Pilates Stabilization with Kelli Roberts (Quick Fix - Pilates ABS Workout) Core Combination with Kelli Roberts (Quick Fix - Pilates ABS Workout) Yoga Flex with Suzanne Douglass (Total Mix: Combination Yoga & Pilates Workout) Yoga Stability with Joy Fitzpatrick (Quick Fix: Power Yoga Workout) Stability Ball with Kelli Roberts (Quick Fix: Stability Ball Workout) Low and Funky with Juliane Arney (Quickfix - Cardio Hip-Hop Workout) Kickbox Core with Janis Saffell (Quick Fix: Total Cardio Kick Total Body Toning with Minna Lessig, Nancy Popp and Julie Upton (Quick Fix - Total Body Toning) In short, if you have ANY of these other videos, you may want to reconsider this purchase as it contains unoriginal material. What a disappointment!
I love how you can customize this DVD. I've done the quick fix tight abs for years, and this is a fun change from my norm that is just as effective.
